information: SDMA is an agricultural equipment distributor: sale of new and used farm equipment from all manufacturers. We are dealers for new VALTRA farming and groundwork equipment. We also offer a full range of hay-making machinery and equipment. SDMA supplies hay-making and ground-working equipment (rakes, tedder rakes, mowers, conditioner mowers, round balers). Other farm equipment: agricultural and forestry tractor.planters, seed drills. Grinder and flail. Flail and brush-cutter. Livestock equipment: cattle truck, silage cutter, silage feed distributor. Feeder. Unpowered ground tools. Plough, disc plough, tine cultivator.Spreaders and manure spreaders. PTO-powered ground tools. Reciprocating harrow. Sprayers.Mounted sprayers. Open space, lawn and garden equipment: chippers, round baler dealer.Livestock equipment.
